878","headword_ar":"وَرَشَ","root":"wr$","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, A, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yari$u","text_ar":"يَرِشُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuruw$N","text_ar":"وُرُوشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waro$N","text_ar":"وَرْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reached,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reached with the hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with the extended hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K,) food, (A, K,) or somewhat thereof, (S,) or a little thereof. (AZ.) ―         -b2-  Also, (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waro$N","text_ar":"وَرْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wuruw$N","text_ar":"وُرُوشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate vehemently and greedily:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, A, K:) but accord. to IAar,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawo$N","text_ar":"رَوْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the rá first, signifies the “ eating much; ” and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waro$N","text_ar":"وَرْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with the wáw first, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"eating little."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, (K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waro$N","text_ar":"وَرْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He coveted; longed; yearned; eagerly desired; strove to acquire; obtain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"attain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wara$a A_ilyhi","text_ar":"وَرَشَ اـِليهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He coveted it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c. (TK.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wara$a","text_ar":"وَرَشَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohimo","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (A, K,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waro$N","text_ar":"وَرْشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He came in to them uninvited when they were eating,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to get some of their food:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and when one has gone in to others while they were drinking, you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wagala Ealyohimo","text_ar":"وَغَلَ عَليْهِمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": but see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAri$N","text_ar":"وَارِشٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wara$a fulaAnFA bifulAanK","text_ar":"وَرَشَ فُلَانًا بِفُلاَنٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He incited such a one against such a one:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-'Abbád, TA:) in the K, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wara$a fulaAnN bifulaAnK","text_ar":"وَرَشَ فُلَانٌ بِفُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) See also 2."}],"source_refs":["S","A","K","TA"]}]}}